  "title": "Management Trainee (Sales & Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>Looking for Something More Than a 9–5 job?</p>\n<p>Euphoria assists clients by managing and executing their preferred channels through face-to-face marketing.</p>\n<p>If you love meeting new people, and want to gain real-world skills while having fun. This is for you!🚀</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<p>💬 Represent clients in exciting campaigns</p>\n<p>🎪 Engage customers at events &amp; roadshows</p>\n<p>🤝 Build connections through face-to-face interactions</p>\n<p>📈 Learn the ropes of sales, marketing &amp; leadership</p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Personal &amp; career growth opportunities</p>\n<p>✅ Fun, youthful &amp; supportive team culture</p>\n<p>✅ Travel opportunities (international exposure)</p>\n<p>✅ Mentorship from experienced leaders</p>\n<p>✅ Incentives &amp; bonuses</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>No experience? No problem. We provide hands-on training to get you started!</p>\n<p>📍 Location: Central Singapore</p>\n<p>📅 Full-time / Part time opportunities available</p>\n<p>Take the first step — build your confidence, skills &amp; future with us!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>👉 Apply now &amp; we will contact you shortly</strong></p>",
